metadata.name: Aoki Gamers #1
metadata.description: Aoki Gamers is not only a PFP, is the access to the Exclusive Egyptian Project we are going to Launch in September, Access to an Exclusive Gaming Community, Access to Free Mint Projects created in House especially for the Community FIRST! We do not define Aoki by a single word, it's simply not a project one can summarize in a short sentence is all about the POWER OF GAMING COMMUNITY. Rather we orient ourselves in the direction where we can fill in the gaps within the NFT world. One primarily being the art. Aoki encourages the gamers out there, creates opportunities and teaches artists and all art admirers to take the best from their experience in this space because Together we will make a difference here!
